---
title: Easy Hearty Beef Rump & Capsicum Goulash with Rapid Rice & Sour Cream
description: No matter the weather, a hearty goulash with spiced beef rump and veggies will go down a treat. Enjoy it with fluffy rice to soak up all
the sauce and a dollop of sour cream on top to give it those cooler tones. It’s a warm, comforting hug in a bowl!
